Nollywood star, Ikechukwu ‘IK’ Ogbonna marked his birthday on Tuesday and his friends and colleagues took to their Instagram pages to celebrate the actor. Announcing his birthday in the early hours of the day, the actor shared a picture of himself with the caption, “+1”. Celebrating the actor, his friend and fellow Nollywood star, Alexx Ekubo, shared a funny picture on his Instagram page with the caption, “Happy Birthday @ikogbonna I’m so proud of your hair journey. You’ve really come a long way. Keep growing and glowing.” Celebrity tailor, Yomi Makun, popularly known as Yomi Casual also celebrated the actor as he joked about Ogbonna’s age. He wrote, “I never guessed that when we first met, we’d become good friends and make lots of amazing memories together! Thanks for all the fun adventures/business deals fam. Here’s to many more in the coming year! “Now It’s OK to light the candles on your birthday cake; I’ve already alerted the fire department! Happy 50th birthday uncle Iyke!” Other celebrities who celebrated the actor’s birthday include actress Lily Afegbua, Shaffy Bello, Lilian Esoro, and others. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com